gcg - Codeforces' contest file structure generator.

Usage:
    gcg init <task-name>        initialize tasks, or specified task by clipping tests
    gcg run <task-name>         compile and run task on tests in folder 'tests'
    gcg help                    print this text

Flags and parameters:
    r, run:
        -t <test-name>          run program on specified test
        -f <folder-name>        run program on all tests in folder <folder-name>
        --no-compile            disable compilation before running tests
    i, init:
        --overwrite             overwrite existing files
        --no-interactive        create <n> tasks and <m> blank tests for each task, where:
            --tasks <m>          
            --tests <n>          
        --no-log                disable logging